<bioghist altrender="biography" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
<head>Biography</head>
<p><persname>Arline Baum</persname> is a <geogname>Connecticut</geogname> children's literature author of <title render="italic">Opt, An Illusionary Tale</title>. The book was illustrated by her husband, <persname>Joseph Baum</persname>.</p>
</bioghist>
<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
<head>Scope and Content</head>
<p>Collection consists of original artwork for or manuscripts of two titles: <title render="italic">Opt, An Illusionary Tale</title> and <title render="italic">One Bright Morning</title>.</p>
</scopecontent>
